    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8069-bf5a-fa4aeedf8c85",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper presents an overall framework that meant to combine different learning analytics activities in a single framework. The authors focus on inter-operability standards and discuss different challenges relating with application and inter-operability.",
